				<td colspan="2"><span>Hello,  I'm looking for hunting suggestions.
<br />

<br />
My friend has a 65 necro and I have a 58 Bard.
<br />
we would like to do some hunting together.
<br />
Can anyone supply me with some suggestions and strategies for duo hunting with a necro.
<br />

<br />
Thanks
<br />

<br />
Velfimere</span></td>
