				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: duo suggestions Bard and Necro<a name="34842"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 15 04 2:31 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>
<br />
Pretty much anything that moves.
<br />

<br />
Bard can keep Necro happy by just singing mana song.  Also bard can use slow song and let the necro pet tank.
<br />

<br />
Some really good XP grinding spots that you should be able to handle with no problems:
<br />

<br />
Halls of Honor Basement
<br />
Plane of Storms (frogs)
<br />

<br />
For pure cash and a little XP to boot:
<br />
Droga : With that combo you should be able to pull and clear a rotation of 4 or maybe 5 named.
<br />
Veksar: Just about anywhere in here is good.
<br />

<br />
Or, get one more level 58 person and go duo LDoN normals.  The other person can drop out before adventure starts so as to avoid loss statistics.  You may not win a lot, but XP should be really good.  Loot not bad either</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
