				<td colspan="2"><span>Outdoors, fear kiting works great because your DOT twist is going to stack and improve with the necro's.
<br />

<br />
Indoors will be a bit tougher - Slow, Replenish and anything you like that will improve your melee and/or debuff the mob. A strong possibility will be to double pull, Charm 1 to attack 2, then add skelly. 2 Should die with 1 at around half health who will be easy to finish off at that point.</span></td>
