				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: duo suggestions Bard and Necro<a name="34879"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 15 04 4:40 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Necros are my favorite class to duo with.  Bard + Necro is a very potent combo.
<br />

<br />
First, our Manasong is doubly effective on Necros.  HP = mana to them, and our song gives both regen and mana.  Not that Necros go OOM often, but when they do a Bard really helps them get FM fast.
<br />

<br />
Next, we can tank stuff that summons and Necro heals + our Slow is usually good enough to get the job done (within reason, obviously some mobs are going to require the whole tank/cleric business).  The rest of the time, just DoT for the added DPS and either Fearkite or let the pet tank, or just Root.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"><hr size="1" align="left" width="15%"><center>Impresario <a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=111714>Keiz Dinzyar</a><br>65 Maestro<br><a href=http://sleinad.homestead.com/files/KeizUI/KeizUI.html><img border=0 src=http://sleinad.homestead.com/files/quote03.jpg></a></center></span></td>
