				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: duo suggestions Bard and Necro<a name="35242"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 18 04 1:23 AM</span></td>
