				<td colspan="2"><span>Well my main is a 65 Necro and in the largest guild on my server.  Hence, uber to put it mildly.  Now that I have all the aa's and almost every piece of gear I could ever want (d*mn Ugua!) I find myself only playing the Necro to get twink items for the bard and raiding.
<br />

<br />
I enjoy fighting with bards.  Duoing with agro kiting is unbelieveable.  Most of the time I hold the agro with my pet stabbing it from behind in a tight circle so my Bard counter part can sing damage.  On occassion the bard will opt to melee the mobs as well from behind like my pet.  Hey whatever breaks the mobs down fastest.
<br />

<br />
And then again every now and again my bard friends like to hold the agro and just kite around me.  FD being the wonderful thing it is I can dot the bjesus out of the mobs, FD, and sit medding until its time for the next mob -all the while having my pet engaged.  
<br />

<br />
I too think an awesome exping combo is a Necro / Bard.
<br />

<br />
Places to get good exp?  Try PoN, Chardok fear kiting into the wall by the Seargent was always a favorite with the bard pulling, amazing exp until PoP came out.  Agro kiting in HoH or PoV works great with that combo.  
<br />

<br />

<br />
</span></td>
